name: DeepVee
description:
A scenic canyon with a few sections of sculpted sandstone and several downclimbs.

Approach

Off of FR 618.

Descent

A bunch of downclimbs. Some are more challenging than others and may require a handline.

This canyon holds water. Below many of the chutes and other obstacles are pools that depending on water level may take some bushwacking or climbing to fully avoid.

Exit

Back to 618.

Red tape

Beta sites

Trip reports and media

Background

This location was published in December 2022, though it is likely the canyon had been descended prior.
